<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Account Access Notification</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; background-color: #f8fafc; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 30px; }
    .info-box { background-color: #f0f9ff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #10b981; }
    .footer { background-color: #f8fafc; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
    .time { font-weight: 600; color: #059669; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>🔐 Account Access Notification</h1>
      <p>Successful sign-in to your Tramate account</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello <%= @user.full_name || @user.email %>! 👋</h2>
      
      <p>We're letting you know that your Tramate account was successfully accessed.</p>
      
      <div class="info-box">
        <h3>📊 Sign-in Details:</h3>
        <p><strong>Time:</strong> <span class="time"><%= @signin_time.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p %Z") %></span></p>
        <p><strong>Location:</strong> <%= @location %></p>
        <p><strong>Device:</strong> <%= @user_agent.truncate(100) %></p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="info-box">
        <h3>🛡️ Security Notice:</h3>
        <p>If this wasn't you, please:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Change your password immediately</li>
          <li>Review your account activity</li>
          <li>Contact support if you notice any suspicious activity</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <p>Your account security is our top priority. We monitor all access to help keep your trading activity safe.</p>
      
      <p>Happy Trading!<br>
      The Tramate Team 🎯</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated security notification sent to <%= @user.email %></p>
      <p>© 2024 Tramate. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 